&lt;p&gt;The gcloud tool automatically incremented the serial counter of the SOA record, so the SOA records always shows in both additions and deletions. Google Cloud DNS supported record types: &lt;a href=&#34;https://developers.google.com/cloud-dns/what-is-cloud-dns#supported_record_types&#34; title=&#34;Google cloud dns supported record types&#34;&gt;https://developers.google.com/cloud-dns/what-is-cloud-dns#supported_record_types&lt;/a&gt; You can add all records in one batch. Here is the example of a adding records to Google Cloud DNS:&lt;/p&gt;
